content:
Change Your Intelligent App Settings

You can change settings for your Intelligent App, such as instantly refreshing the app or scheduling an app refresh to be performed later.

To immediately refresh the app, click Refresh App. If you query Salesforce objects, the refresh runs recipes and updates the datasets instead.

To schedule a regular app refresh, click Schedule App Refresh. Select how often and what time to refresh your data. For example, schedule a daily refresh at twelve AM daily. To manually upgrade the app to the newest version of the app template, click Update.

If you schedule an immediate refresh or update your app, go to the Monitoring tab to see how the process is progressing.

The Settings tab displays when the last app refresh ran, when the next app refresh is scheduled, and if a schedule is set.
title: Changing Settings in Salesforce Intelligent Apps
